                <h4 class="icon-title">Instructions</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="icon-box-content">
                <ol>
                  <li>Enter Your name, email, and contact, so the agent can contact you once they have what you want</li><br>
                  <li>Select the type of service you want from the dropdown menu (Rent, Buy, Sell, Lease)</li><br>
                  <li>Enter the description of the type of house you either want to buy, sell, rent, or lease</li><br>
                  <li>Once you're done, click the make request button to send request</li><br>
                </ol>
